release_notes:
This release contains a single change to the behavior of the client when WARP session duration Gateway Network or HTTP policies are in place. No other bug fixes or feature are included.
 
## Notable updates
 
- Modified client behavior to no longer automatically open a new browser tab when user needs to re-authenticate as this was causing some users to return to their devices with 100s of tabs open. Instead the client will now use the built in operating system notification framework to inform users of the need to authenticate.
 
## Known issues
- No known issues
 
For Zero Trust documentation please see: https://developers.cloudflare.com/cloudflare-one/connections/connect-devices/warp
 
For Consumer documentation please see: https://developers.cloudflare.com/warp-client/
